{"tid":2330754,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔想寫求情書，我都冇錯","createTime":"2020-12-18T09:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T13:11:58.000Z","uid":379141,"like":15,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f30da07e49c460f2bdcb539fbe4f7bf616f1aa","tid":2330754,"uid":379141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"臨近判決，律師話要審慎起見叫身邊嘅人寫求情封，自己都要寫一封。身邊嘅人寫乜我冇得理，但要我自己寫，我真係過唔到自己個關，我到底犯左咩錯，我冇做錯過野，點解我要承受我嘅罪名，再向人求情？<br />\n<br />\n我知咩叫忍辱負重，但亦都唔想為半斗米折腰。<br />\n<br />\n我知道結果唔係我自己一個承擔，我屋企人，女朋友，身邊嘅人都會難受。究竟我嘅生命，係要對得住我愛嘅人，定對得住自己？<br />\n<br />\n或者我都係鳩up下，你地可能會話我心底已經有答案，可能係嘅，掛？<br />\n<br />\n唔知開咩台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c86b918421966def1cec4de90d756529e7dd75","tid":2330754,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"冇所謂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />坐多幾個月"},{"pid":"626858f538825e82dead6b7e0ac0de5e35bf93d6","tid":2330754,"uid":10901,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47c86b918421966def1cec4de90d756529e7dd75","tid":2330754,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"冇所謂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />坐多幾個月"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"食屎啦仆街"},{"pid":"dd080e714b7d38b8b65a97d2be8545dbc2e65d4c","tid":2330754,"uid":379141,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"626858f538825e82dead6b7e0ac0de5e35bf93d6","tid":2330754,"uid":10901,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47c86b918421966def1cec4de90d756529e7dd75","tid":2330754,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"冇所謂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />坐多幾個月"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"食屎啦仆街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:18:41.000Z","msg":"其實佢都係講事實<img src=\"/assets